        "cooked": "<p>Greetings everyone, I’ve noticed some inconsistencies in the ui of the arabic version. I know the hardships of working with bidi ui and RTL languages but seeing that most of the ui is coherent with arabic i wanted to highlight these issues.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/9/8/98bfdc442adf65cb0018692801e8e1240f52401b.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/98bfdc442adf65cb0018692801e8e1240f52401b\" title=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-19-44-25-582-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/8/98bfdc442adf65cb0018692801e8e1240f52401b_2_690x329.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-19-44-25-582-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\" data-base62-sha1=\"lNhDlduDyZv1LYiyF8Tf6itxkSL\" width=\"690\" height=\"329\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/8/98bfdc442adf65cb0018692801e8e1240f52401b_2_690x329.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/8/98bfdc442adf65cb0018692801e8e1240f52401b_2_1035x493.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/9/8/98bfdc442adf65cb0018692801e8e1240f52401b.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"4E493D\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_2025-04-03-19-44-25-582-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms</span><span class=\"informations\">1080×516 60.3 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\nThis pictures shows the correct direction of the send arrow.<br>\nBut if you want to share an image, the arrow is flipped( like it should be for LTR ui)<br>\nAnother one is the camera icon in the chat and many other places like when you try to create a  call and many other places. it needs to be flipped too<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/5/5/55fd7b36c0a13ec804fc8808d67ace8a195d0b27.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/55fd7b36c0a13ec804fc8808d67ace8a195d0b27\" title=\"IMG_20250403_214119\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/5/5/55fd7b36c0a13ec804fc8808d67ace8a195d0b27_2_690x192.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_20250403_214119\" data-base62-sha1=\"cgHFiMOx25pvWTSKzbB6TvsilIr\" width=\"690\" height=\"192\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/5/5/55fd7b36c0a13ec804fc8808d67ace8a195d0b27_2_690x192.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/5/5/55fd7b36c0a13ec804fc8808d67ace8a195d0b27_2_1035x288.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/5/5/55fd7b36c0a13ec804fc8808d67ace8a195d0b27.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"6D4839\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_20250403_214119</span><span class=\"informations\">1080×301 43.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Other icons i think should be flipped are the list icon, the speaker icon and there’s like one instance only where the back arrow  icon  is not flipped i think it’s in the menu when you try to change the alias of a contact. I’ll include pictures bellow so you can see what I’m taking about.</p>\n<div class=\"d-image-grid\">\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/e/2e6cd741ded3311196c747727cf26cecfd5bab3d.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/2e6cd741ded3311196c747727cf26cecfd5bab3d\" title=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-03-00-247-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/e/2e6cd741ded3311196c747727cf26cecfd5bab3d_2_690x424.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-03-00-247-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\" data-base62-sha1=\"6CH9yiuTwtqXpjlQ0ZeSKUcDyI5\" width=\"690\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/e/2e6cd741ded3311196c747727cf26cecfd5bab3d_2_690x424.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/e/2e6cd741ded3311196c747727cf26cecfd5bab3d_2_1035x636.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/e/2e6cd741ded3311196c747727cf26cecfd5bab3d.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"212024\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-03-00-247-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms</span><span class=\"informations\">1080×664 61.5 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n</div>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/9/f96fdca6893ee38e846924dcd0c6ad6bbb677735.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/f96fdca6893ee38e846924dcd0c6ad6bbb677735\" title=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-03-39-463-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/9/f96fdca6893ee38e846924dcd0c6ad6bbb677735_2_690x203.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-03-39-463-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\" data-base62-sha1=\"zACyit6kN6pd9rNneKUBcPK6O6F\" width=\"690\" height=\"203\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/9/f96fdca6893ee38e846924dcd0c6ad6bbb677735_2_690x203.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/9/f96fdca6893ee38e846924dcd0c6ad6bbb677735_2_1035x304.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/9/f96fdca6893ee38e846924dcd0c6ad6bbb677735.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"242428\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-03-39-463-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms</span><span class=\"informations\">1080×319 58.7 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/0/4/04ae7abca8c6ffef3669c1732e8069c23c076db9.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/04ae7abca8c6ffef3669c1732e8069c23c076db9\" title=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-04-49-106-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/4/04ae7abca8c6ffef3669c1732e8069c23c076db9_2_690x387.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-04-49-106-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\" data-base62-sha1=\"FpJhvmUOHjK6Zhv4YiUx2r43l7\" width=\"690\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/4/04ae7abca8c6ffef3669c1732e8069c23c076db9_2_690x387.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/4/04ae7abca8c6ffef3669c1732e8069c23c076db9_2_1035x580.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/0/4/04ae7abca8c6ffef3669c1732e8069c23c076db9.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"1F2024\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-04-49-106-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms</span><span class=\"informations\">1080×606 53.6 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/9/8/985b6709fa2a22d76a851b9013e1183a57df51d4.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/985b6709fa2a22d76a851b9013e1183a57df51d4\" title=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-06-15-196-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/8/985b6709fa2a22d76a851b9013e1183a57df51d4_2_690x311.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-06-15-196-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\" data-base62-sha1=\"lJOp4IpTGfYpdPjfIVJbZkJdBHK\" width=\"690\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/8/985b6709fa2a22d76a851b9013e1183a57df51d4_2_690x311.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/8/985b6709fa2a22d76a851b9013e1183a57df51d4_2_1035x466.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/9/8/985b6709fa2a22d76a851b9013e1183a57df51d4.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"222023\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-06-15-196-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms</span><span class=\"informations\">1080×487 45.5 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Last but not least, when i try to share say a YouTube video and the alias of a contact is in english it gets crammed next to the radio button i think this needs fixing too.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/a/0/a02adb8993fb4984d87b98e7ba7dfd29fe8682ad.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/a02adb8993fb4984d87b98e7ba7dfd29fe8682ad\" title=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-10-50-964-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/0/a02adb8993fb4984d87b98e7ba7dfd29fe8682ad_2_400x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-10-50-964-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms\" data-base62-sha1=\"mQUdsRWPOYogGMPUaKNTlNzoqpD\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/0/a02adb8993fb4984d87b98e7ba7dfd29fe8682ad_2_400x500.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/0/a02adb8993fb4984d87b98e7ba7dfd29fe8682ad_2_600x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/0/a02adb8993fb4984d87b98e7ba7dfd29fe8682ad_2_800x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"262427\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_2025-04-03-20-10-50-964-edit_org.thoughtcrime.securesms</span><span class=\"informations\">1080×1348 133 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\nPheew, that’s a lot i guess but i hope the team fixes these issues.thank you everyone for the hard work keep it going.</p>\n<p>EDIT:<br>\nThere’s a neat video from apple</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022/10034/\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/a/2/a2f13a66e4c2096d7ad053f638bcbbc86061cd6b.png\" class=\"site-icon\" data-dominant-color=\"A3CFFF\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022/10034/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Apple Developer</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:500/282;\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/d/f/dfd0a7b0a83c939d94f826d575f1f6b69412eaaf.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" data-dominant-color=\"553E42\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022/10034/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Design for Arabic - WWDC22 - Videos - Apple Developer</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Find out how to design or optimize your app or game for Arabic. Whether you're planning a first release or improving an existing app or...</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>about designing for the arabic layout, it goes into the nitty gritty details of changing the direction of layout items, how to handle fonts and they even went the distance to create icon variants that work well with arabic.</p>\n<p>I also don’t get it why my chat bubble is at the left side, it throws me off a lot. Given that Arabic is a RTL language it’s more intuitive for the bubble to be at the right hand side.</p>",
