        "created_at": "2025-05-25T19:07:33.261Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This is how it’s supposed to work, Arabic is a RTL language, so the message that you want to read is on the right (e.g the message the was sent to you) and your messages that you read later is in the left.</p>\n<p>Because we read from the right and the sender’s messages are supposed to be in the right edge of the screen so the current behavior is correct</p>",
